# Contributing

## Purpose

This repository is intended to evolve in a structured way.  
Contributors should prioritize clarity, maintainability, and product coherence.

## Basic Rules

- keep pull requests focused
- do not mix unrelated changes
- update docs when behavior or structure changes
- avoid adding complexity without clear value
- preserve product direction defined in the docs folder

## Before Changing Code

Review:

- `README.md`
- `AGENTS.md`
- `docs/product-requirements.md`
- `docs/architecture.md`
- `docs/mvp-scope.md`

## Frontend Expectations

- maintain visual consistency
- respect the design system
- do not introduce random UI patterns
- avoid overcrowded screens
- prefer reusable components

## Product Expectations

- generated BPMN is a draft, not guaranteed truth
- structured user input is a first-class part of the product
- BPMN and planning metadata must remain connected
- MVP scope must be respected

## Pull Request Checklist

- [ ] change is scoped and understandable
- [ ] documentation updated if needed
- [ ] no unnecessary dependencies introduced
- [ ] product direction still consistent
- [ ] UI remains coherent with brand rules
